  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A marathon rally unfolds at the kitchen line, with both players showcasing incredible patience and control. After a prolonged exchange of dinks, the player in the grey hoodie finds an opening and unleashes a powerful speed-up to win the point.",
