    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we have witnessed a rather lengthy exchange of pickleball volleys. It's quite remarkable, really. The players were so focused, I almost forgot to breathe. Almost. But then, one of them decided to, you know, *hit it hard*. And that, my friends, is how you win. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
    "chuck_norris_voice": "Chuck Norris once played a rally this long, and the ball is still in play somewhere in the universe.",
